snippet.title: Wytchwood | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Grab your grimoire and gather your potions, the time to craft your spells approaches! Though you forget, a deal was made, and you've a debt yet to be paid...

Prepare for an allegorical crafting adventure when AlientrapGames' Wytchwood launches, December 9th!

PlayStation | Xbox | Nintendo Switch | Steam | Epic Games

Wishlist on Steam: https://cozygames.pub/wytchwood-steam

Follow on Twitter to get updates!
Alientrap Games: https://twitter.com/AlientrapGames
Whitethorn Games: https://twitter.com/WhitethornGames
